==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mammee tree
<hw>Mam*mee" tree`</hw></mhw> <pr>(?)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Haitian <ets>mamey</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A fruit tree of tropical America, belonging to the genus
<gen>Mammea</gen> (<spn>Mammea Americana</spn>); also, its fruit, called
the <prod>mammee apple</prod>. The latter is large, covered with a
thick, tough ring, and contains a bright yellow pulp of a pleasant taste
and fragrant scent. It is often called <altname>mammee
apple</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> mammee apple, mammee, mamey, <spn>Mammea
americana</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>mammee apple</ent>⟦br⟧
